## 🎨 Professional UI Design & Color Scheme

To meet the "professional UI" requirement, NovaMart will feature a highly polished, modern, premium aesthetic. No generic Bootstrap looks.

### The "Nova" Theme (Dark Mode Default)

-   **Style**: Premium Dark Mode with Neon/Holo Accents, heavy use of Glassmorphism (frosted glass effects).
-   **Typography**:
    -   Headings: `Outfit` (Geometric, modern, bold)
    -   Body text: `Inter` (Highly readable, clean)
-   **Micro-interactions**: Hover lifts, smooth color transitions, interactive buttons, sleek modal animations.

### Finalized Color Palette

| Usage | Color Hex | Description |
|---|---|---|
| **Background (Deep Space)** | `#0B0E14` | Very dark, slightly blue-tinted gray. Better than pure black. |
| **Surface (Frosted Glass)** | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03)` | For cards and panels, accompanied by `backdrop-filter: blur(10px)`. |
| **Primary Accent (Nova Purple)** | `#8A2BE2` | Vibrant Blue-Violet. Used for primary buttons and active states. |
| **Secondary Accent (Cyan/Teal)** | `#00E5FF` | Electric Cyan. Used for hover states, badges, and small highlights. |
| **Text Primary** | `#F8FAFC` | Crisp white for readability. |
| **Text Secondary** | `#94A3B8` | Muted silver-gray for secondary info. |
| **Status: Success** | `#10B981` | Emerald Green (Order Confirmed, In Stock). |
| **Status: Error/Cancel** | `#EF4444` | Crimson Red (Errors, Cancelled Orders). |
| **Status: Warning/Pending**| `#F59E0B` | Amber (Pending actions, low stock). |

