## 🗺️ Build Phases

### Phase 1 — Backend & DB Setup (Local Mongo)
- Init project, install packages (including `socket.io`).
- Setup Mongoose connection to local `mongodb://localhost:27017/novamart`.
- Define Schemas & run Seed script.
- Build JWT Auth routes & middleware.

### Phase 2 — API & Socket Architecture
- Build all REST API controllers (Products, Cart, Orders, Admin).
- Integrate `Socket.io` with Express server.
- Setup event emitters in controllers (e.g., `io.emit('newOrder')` when order placed).

### Phase 3 — Store Frontend (Premium UI)
- Implement the "Nova" design system CSS.
- Build pages: Home, Product Details, Cart, Checkout, Auth, Profile.
- Connect to API and add Socket.IO client listeners (`orderStatusUpdate`).

### Phase 4 — Separate Admin Panel
- Build Admin dark theme CSS.
- Admin Auth logic & Dashboard stats.
- Connect Admin Socket.IO client (`newOrder` notifications).
- Order Management UI (change status -> triggers socket event to customer).

### Phase 5 — Final Polish
- Ensure all hover effects, toasts, and transitions match the premium requirement.
- Verify end-to-end Socket real-time flow.
- Code cleanup and brief instructions.

